{"word":"G5221 - ὑπαντάω - hypantáō - hoop-an-tah'-o - Meet","slug":"G5221","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπαντάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypantáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-an-tah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Meet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - hupantao&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-an-tah'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G473\">G473</a>; to <i>go opposite</i> (<i>meet</i>) <i>under</i> (<i>quietly</i>), that is, to <i>encounter</i>, <i>fall in with:</i> - (go to) meet."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2658\">G2658</a>, <a href=\"#/G5222\">G5222</a>"}]}